                <h1>Understanding Richard Ramirez: A Look into His Childhood</h1>
                <p>Richard Ramirez, born in 1960, experienced a tumultuous childhood marked by violence and instability. Growing up in a dysfunctional family, he was exposed to his cousins' criminal behavior and suffered abuse from his father. These early experiences profoundly impacted his psyche and contributed to his future criminal actions as the notorious Night Stalker.</p>
